And look at this gear shifter,

06:01.390 --> 06:03.910
all the mechanism is exposed so
you can see the workings. It is

06:04.710 --> 06:06.790
made from 67 different parts,
all arranged just

06:07.630 --> 06:10.830
so you can hear that mechanical
clunk of a gear being selected.

06:11.630 --> 06:13.590
You don't even need to use it,
you can use the paddles by the wheel

06:14.270 --> 06:17.070
but they have put that there because-
it makes it more of an occasion.

06:22.510 --> 06:27.270
This fanatical attention to detail
goes on and on and on.

06:28.070 --> 06:30.870
Even the body is more high-tech
than the one you will

06:31.630 --> 06:33.750
find on a Formula One car.

06:37.070 --> 06:40.270
It is made from carbotanium.
I even know what that means!

06:40.950 --> 06:42.350
