a more traditional single plate
clutch because it is smaller

07:16.390 --> 07:18.190
and a whole 100 kilograms lighter.

07:21.790 --> 07:25.710
In fact, the Huayra
weighs just 1,350 kilograms

07:27.070 --> 07:32.230
and has the power-to-weight ratio
of 541 brake horsepower per ton.

07:33.070 --> 07:35.710
That is more than you get
from a Bugatti Veyron.

07:37.630 --> 07:41.110
