to keep everything stable.

08:47.790 --> 08:48.750
That is astonishing!

08:54.030 --> 08:55.590
All from the back wheels,
I am in love!

08:56.630 --> 08:59.430
But the handling is not
all down to the magic flaps.

09:01.070 --> 09:02.990
It doesn't feel big,
like a Lambo,

09:03.950 --> 09:05.870
