corner it without hiding in the
glovebox, whimpering.

09:16.310 --> 09:18.830
Oh, God,
this is properly put together.

09:22.150 --> 09:25.070
The Zonda was always going to be
a difficult act to follow,

09:25.630 --> 09:27.710
